Iron Chef America - Season 12, Episode 8




Grill Masters: U.S.A. vs. Australia

Team USA (Iron Chefs Bobby Flay, Marc Forgione and Alex Guarnaschelli) battles Team Australia (Chefs Adrian Richardson, Darren Robertson and Tobie Puttock) in a Grill Masters competition. The judges are Donatella Arpaia, Ryan Kwanten and Elizabeth Karmel.




Original Air Date: 25-May-2014
